OL,6,FUnder-performing civil servants could
OL,7,Fbe incentivised to leave their jobs
OL,8,Fand senior officials will have their
OL,9,Fpay linked to performance, under new
OL,10,Fgovernment plans to "fundamentally
OL,11,Freshape" the service.
OL,13,FCabinet Office minister Pat McFadden
OL,14,Fhas said that "the state is not match-
OL,15,Ffit to rise to the moment our country
OL,16,Ffaces" as he said the changes aim to
OL,17,Fproduce a "more focused and productive
OL,18,Fcivil service."
