OL,3,CUnder-performing civil servants could
OL,4,Cbe incentivised to leave their jobs
OL,6,F"We want a performance framework that
OL,7,Freally rewards excellent performance.
OL,8,FAnd where it doesn't, we can have some
OL,9,Fvoluntary exit and some mutually
OL,10,Fagreed exit."
OL,12,FHe added that the reason behind the
OL,13,Fdecision "is to make sure that funds
OL,14,Fgo where people really want them to
OL,15,Fgo", such as hiring more teachers and
OL,16,Fgetting hospital waiting lists down.
OL,18,FIt is one in a series of reforms
OL,19,Fexpected to be set out by the
OL,20,Fgovernment this week that will also
OL,21,Fcover housing and regulation.
