OL,3,CUnder-performing civil servants could
OL,4,Cbe incentivised to leave their jobs
OL,6,FThey will go alongside what officials
OL,7,Fare calling an "intervention" from the
OL,8,Fprime minister on Thursday.
OL,10,FIn the plans to be announced by
OL,11,FMcFadden at the start of the week, he
OL,12,Fwill promise a new "mutually agreed
OL,13,Fexits" process, in which civil
OL,14,Fservants who cannot perform at the
OL,15,Flevel required of them are
OL,16,Fincentivised to leave their jobs.
OL,18,FThe system will be designed to give
OL,19,Fbosses more tools to address bad
OL,20,Fperformance.
