OL,3,CUnder-performing civil servants could
OL,4,Cbe incentivised to leave their jobs
OL,6,FAlongside the exit processes, senior
OL,7,Fcivil servants who are not meeting
OL,8,Fstandards will be put on development
OL,9,Fplans, with a view to being sacked if
OL,10,Fthere is no improvement within six
OL,11,Fmonths, and the most senior officials
OL,12,Fwill have their pay linked to
OL,13,Fperformance outcomes.
OL,15,FHe will also pledge to increase the
OL,16,Fgovernment's digital capabilities,
OL,17,Fwith more staff to be employed in
OL,18,Frelevant roles, and more public
OL,19,Fservices to be digitised.
